Senior/System Engineers (PSS/201401/01/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00006306
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Jan 10 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Design and develop Functional and Detailed Design Specifications for hardware and software.
Setting up hardware and software for medium to large-sized Distributed Control Systems (DCS) and other project related systems.
Testing of hardware and software for medium to large-sized DCS and other project related systems.
Coordinate and interface to third party vendor/systems.
Software configuration and programming of medium to large-sized DCS and other project related systems.
Perform project and engineering documentation/ factory acceptance test / site installation / site acceptance test / site commissioning etc.
Requirements:
Degree/Diploma in Electrical, Electronics, Chemical, Mechanical, Control or Computer Engineering with minimum 6 years working experience.
Knowledge in Process Control preferable; have initiative, good interpersonal & communication skills.
Willing to travel.